UPDIKE, Respondent, v. ELMIRA BLDG. CO. et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Alvah N. Updike against the Elmira Building' Company and others.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
